Title: Wild Cherry
Writer: Grant Vetters, David Kolbowicz, Chris Charney, Chris Charney (screenplay)
Actors: Rumer Willis, Tania Raymonde, Kristin Cavallari, Ryan Merriman
Plot: A virginal high school senior decides to get revenge on her jock boyfriend when she discovers he's only dating her in hopes that she'll end up in his team's "bang book."
